        public static void bindObjViewFrame(Context context,
                    DatabaseManager db,
                    ViewGroup frame,
                    DbObjCursorAdapter.ViewHolder viewHolder,
                    DbObjCursorAdapter.DbObjCursor objRow)
        Binds the generic frame of a feed object. This method is not threadsafe.
        Parameters:
        v - the view to bind
        context - standard activity context
        c - the cursor source for the object in the db object table. Must include _id in the projection.
        allowInteractions - controls whether the bound view is allowed to intercept touch events and do its own processing.
